    "Id": "746577",
    "ThreadId": "294645",
    "Html": "<p>if e.MidiEvent is an instance of NoteEvent, cast it to a NoteEvent, and then you have access to the NoteNumber property which is an int</p>\r\n<p>if e.MidiEvent is an instance of ControlChangeEvent, cast it to a ControlChangeEvent, and then you have access to the ControllerValue property which is an int</p>\r\n<p>The NAudioDemo app is just using the MidiEvent ToString(), but there is no reason for you to use it if you don't like the format it displays data in.</p>",
