    "Html": "<p>Mark i cnat udnerstadn how do, i follow teh example, yes. and do this:<br /><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">void</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"> midiIn_MessageReceived(</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">object</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"> sender, </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\">MidiInMessageEventArgs</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"> <span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">e) <br />{<br /></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\">MessageBox</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">.Show(</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #2b91af; font-size: x-small;\">Convert</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">.ToString(e.MidiEvent));<span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"> <br /></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">}<br /><br />Can showme with a code example&nbsp;how can acces to only INT values:<br />MIDI CHANNEL<br />MIDI NOTE<br />VALUE<br /><br />and also<br /><br />MIDI CHANEL<br />MIDI CC<br />VALUE<br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">Thankyou for your patience, and please apologize i not understand what you explain.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>",
